  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/fadd3963e038ffeed10db373c9839908.poster.avif?t=1698257356\" width=640 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/fadd3963e038ffeed10db373c9839908.webm?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/fadd3963e038ffeed10db373c9839908.mp4?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>FROM FEAR</strong> is a 1-4 player online co-op survival horror where you choose your fear. Collect resources, unlock new maps and tools, all while trying to stay alive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR FEAR</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/175307224db7b5022eb717d6973c064c.poster.avif?t=1698257356\" width=640 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/175307224db7b5022eb717d6973c064c.webm?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/175307224db7b5022eb717d6973c064c.mp4?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Fear is personal</strong> - Choose your own and let the game adapt to <strong>your</strong> fear.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Monster and loot determined by fear.<br></li><li> Unique experiences, even across multiplayer.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MONSTER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/1d14e123f71241cd4894728b78bb3fa9.poster.avif?t=1698257356\" width=640 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/1d14e123f71241cd4894728b78bb3fa9.webm?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/1d14e123f71241cd4894728b78bb3fa9.mp4?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Hide from your fear</strong> - Stay out of their way or be hunted down.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unpredictable AI - No game will be the same.<br></li><li> Use the environment to lure the monster.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT RESOURCES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/7729739e3afbded35e3e132c2c43c56a.poster.avif?t=1698257356\" width=640 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/7729739e3afbded35e3e132c2c43c56a.webm?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/7729739e3afbded35e3e132c2c43c56a.mp4?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect resources to unlock new maps and characters.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Items found are broken down into one or more resources.<br></li><li> Find the fuel or remain stranded.<br></li><li> Discover keys to unlock new areas.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-4 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/210472c7e9ddf265df0e7e43f796b586.poster.avif?t=1698257356\" width=636 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/210472c7e9ddf265df0e7e43f796b586.webm?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/210472c7e9ddf265df0e7e43f796b586.mp4?t=1698257356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Face your fears alone or with friends</strong> - Will you help or leave them behind?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Heal wounded allies or let them bleed out.<br></li><li> When cornered, use your friends as bait.</li></ul>",
